==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Eisteddfod
<hw>Eis*tedd"fod</hw> <pr>(⟦amac⟧s*t⟦ecr⟧⟦th⟧"v⟦omac⟧d)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[W., session, fr. <ets>eistedd</ets> to sit.]</ety>
<def>An assembly or session of the Welsh bards; an annual congress of
bards, minstrels and literati of Wales, -- being a patriotic revival of
the old custom.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Either</ent>⟦br⟧
